Package: dnsplane
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: DNS resolver with local records and optional DoT/DoH
 dnsplane answers DNS queries with optional local records, upstream
 forwarding, adblock, and clustering. This package installs the server
 binary and a systemd unit using /usr/bin/dnsplane (see
 /usr/share/doc/dnsplane/README.packaging or upstream packaging/README.md).
